message:
The world is a miserable place, but at least Enna Alouette exists.' 

I've watched plenty of YouTube videos, but none of them were able to make me genuinely laugh except for yours, Enna! I've never thought that after a dreadul day, I was excited to watch your videos that bring joy to me. I too think, that the world is a miserable place and often wish that I was just a cat, but you are one of the reasons why I continue to do what I have to do. I enjoy your negative talks about life (especially during the trial by trolley collab), perhaps because I relate to those negative thoughts too. But of course, I wish you well and hope that lesser negative thoughts surround you!  

Thank you for bringing joy to Aloupeeps, Enna! I wish you good health, and I wish you to have a great life, because you have brought joy to thousands! Thank you for being part of Ethyria, and being part of Nijisanji! 

Happy 1 year anniversary Ethyria!
